Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/erikfercak/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Build ruby extension:
    cd ~/.vim/bundle/command-t
    rake make
